,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T07:12:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>6月先開，一開始10蚊<br />\n輸完再買大d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n早排追返，唔敢再玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/21/115046_ab0643ef06c35fa154a9aa0c0a730feb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F21%2F115046_ab0643ef06c35fa154a9aa0c0a730feb.jpg&h=1cd1776c&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n點樣可以夠膽一場50k<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都想追返</blockquote><br />\n仲要直插主客和唔買盤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1547c4234ba07f59d3b7707e905eaa58b2f9b155","tid":407370,"uid":71160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T08:41:41.000Z","msg":"當機立斷去馬會cut撚左佢，發誓唔會再申請，否則死全家"},{"pid":"54d6945e8a07bb904cc1ce4f9514c2b4e418d18b","tid":407370,"uid":5946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T08:53:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>戒了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n每日戒一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n渣ga,諗方法戒,每人的方法都唔同,搵個合你心水既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n師兄用咩方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我開始逼自已一個月入500蚊玩,個銀行ac只放500,唔俾自已自動轉帳，一個月輸哂就無,有特就拎出黎,所以賭得好細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可能因為10蚊-50蚊咁玩,一個月通常唔會輸哂(一日只玩最多2場),慢慢就唔係點賭了。<br />\n<br />\n但記得唔好自已諗貼士,去波post搵1-2場心水就算</blockquote><br />\n本來有400本，贏到一千，拎六百出黎，又係400重新黎過"},{"pid":"c8eece7f641a7180db2ef679fff57a3c6cae62c4","tid":407370,"uid":80183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T08:56:02.000Z","msg":"其實大家唔好用app<br />\n真金白銀俾錢就會俾少好多<img src=\"/as